<title>yswʿ mạ ạ̉ḥlạk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ( lm ạkn ạ̉ʿlm ạny sạ̉lqạk wtrwy nfsy mn rw̉yạk
 wạ̉ny sạdẖwb fyk wfy sknạk yswʿ yswʿ mạ ạ̉ḥlạk )2
 ạlqrạr - ( bḥtẖt ʿny ạ̹dẖ ạ̉nt ṣdyq llḍʿfạʾ rfyq drb ạ̹lh ḥnạn llbsṭạʾ )2
 ( jn mn ybḥtẖ ʿn frḥ lhlạk yswʿ yswʿ mạ ạ̉ḥlạk )2
 2- ( lst wḥdy mn gẖny̱ fy smạk wrfʿ ạltsbyḥ lʿlạk
 ạ̉nt bry wfrḥ ạlqlb wạlrwḥ fdạk yswʿ yswʿ mạ ạ̉ḥlạk )2</lyrics>
